finance-sync dry-run
finance-sync export-csv
finance-sync monthly-summary

Claude integration:
Build a lightweight local API layer or MCP-compatible interface allowing Claude Desktop to:
- query summaries
- inspect categorized transactions
- answer budgeting questions
- generate reports

Claude should only receive:
- sanitized transaction data
- aggregated summaries
- never credentials or raw auth tokens

